**Formula One activities of Mercedes-Benz**

This particular discourse centers on [Mercedes](/Mercedes-Benz) as an active [Formula One](/Formula_One) constructor. For an exploration into Mercedes’ role as a mere engine supplier, one should direct their attention to [Ilmor](/Ilmor) (active from 1991–1994) and the more recent iteration, [Mercedes AMG High Performance Powertrains](/Mercedes_AMG_High_Performance_Powertrains) (from 1994 onwards). It's a distinction that, for some, remains stubbornly elusive.

